public_note_tsim: Coin clipped. Due to clipping, date that would have been in exergue has been cut out, making identification problematic. However, style would position coin within the first reign of Antiochus VIII at Antioch. Another mark for attribution to this type is the [Ι]Ε visible on the outer left and the lack of secondary controls in the exergue.
